            <h3 class="text-[2rem] font-medium text-gray-800  mt-2">Who we are to Serve the nation</h3>
            <!-- Short Description -->
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">
                We are dedicated to bringing you the latest and most inspiring stories from around the world. Our mission is to inform, inspire, and connect readers through meaningful content.
            </p>
            <!-- Services Features -->
            <div class="mt-6">
                <p class="flex items-center text-gray-700 mb-2">
                    <span class="text-blue-500 mr-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i></span> High-quality journalism.
