                        <p class="ml-4 text-gray-700 text-lg">
                            Expand our reach to connect communities worldwide.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="flex-shrink-0 text-blue-500 text-2xl">
                            <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                        </span>
                        <p class="ml-4 text-gray-700 text-lg">
                            Innovate and embrace new storytelling formats for the modern audience.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Achievements Section -->
            <div class="bg-white shadow-xl rounded-lg p-8 flex flex-col transform transition duration-500 hover:scale-105" data-aos="fade-left">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Achievements</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                    We’re proud of the recognition and milestones we've earned through our hard work and dedication.
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-6">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="flex-shrink-0 text-green-500 text-2xl">
                            <i class="fas fa-award"></i>
                        </span>
                        <p class="ml-4 text-gray-700 text-lg">
                            Recognized as the leading digital magazine of the year.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="flex-shrink-0 text-green-500 text-2xl">
                            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
